ment<ref name=\"insight-Sept2018\" />\n| $80\u2013100 million<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/box-office/shazam-box-office-opening-weekend-pet-sematary-1203177258/|title=Box Office: 'Shazam!' Heads Toward $45 Million-Plus Opening Weekend|last=Rubin|first=Rebecca|last2=Rubin|first2=Rebecca|date=2019-04-03|website=Variety|language=en|access-date=2019-04-04}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/03/shazam-pet-sematary-projected-box-office-opening-1202575628/|title='Shazam!' Looks To Strike Lightning With $45M Opening; 'Pet Sematary' Eyes Mid $20M+ \u2013 Early Tracking|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|last2=D'Alessandro|first2=Anthony|date=2019-03-14|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2019-04-04}}</ref>\n| $365.9 million<ref name=\"BOM3\">{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=untitledmovieiv.htm|title=''Shazam!'' (2019)|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=April 7, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Joker (2019 film)|Joker]]''\n| [[Todd Phillips]]\n| Todd Phillips and [[Scott Silver]]\n| ''[[Joker (character)|Joker]]'' by Bill Finger, Bob Kane and Jerry Robinson\n| Warner Bros. Pictures / Sikelia Productions / Joint Effort / DC Entertainment<ref name=\"insight-Sept2018\" />\n| $55\u201370 million<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=joker2019.htm |title=Joker (2019) |website=[[Box Office Mojo]] |access-date=December 22, 2019}}</ref>\n| $1.074 billion<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Joker-(2019)#tab=box-office |title=Joker (2019) |website=[[The Numbers (website)|The Numbers]] |access-date=December 22, 2019}}</ref>\n|- \n| 2020\n| ''[[Birds of Prey (2020 film)|Birds of Prey]]''\n|  [[Cathy Yan]]\n| [[Christina Hodson]]\n| ''[[Birds of Prey (comics)|Birds of Prey]]'' by [[Jordan B. Gorfinkel]] and [[Chuck Dixon]]\n| Warner Bros. Pictures / DC Films / LuckyChap Entertainment / Kroll & Co. Entertainment / Clubhouse Pictures\n| $82\u2013100 million<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=BirdsOfPrey2020.htm |title=Birds Of Prey (2020) |website=[[Box Office Mojo]] |access-date=February 29, 2020}}</ref>\n| $179.5 million<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/BirdsOfPrey-(2019)#tab=box-office |title=Birds Of Prey (2020) |website=[[The Numbers (website)|The Numbers]] |access-date=February 29, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|- style=\"background:#b0c4de;\"\n! colspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | Upcoming films\n! colspan=\"2\" |Status\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2020\n|-\n| ''[[Wonder Woman 1984]]''\n| Patty Jenkins\n| '''Story by''' Patty Jenkins and Geoff Johns<br />'''Screenplay by''' Patty Jenkins, Geoff Johns and [[David Callaham]]\n| {{based on|''Wonder Woman''|William Moulton Marston}}\n| Warner Bros. Pictures / Cruel and Unusual Films / Mandy Films / DC Entertainment / Atlas Entertainment / Mad Ghost Productions<ref name=insight-Sept2018/>\n| colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" | Post-production\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2021\n| ''[[The Batman (film)|The Batman]]''\n| [[Matt Reeves]]\n| Matt Reeves & [[Mattson Tomlin]]\n| {{based on|''Batman''|Bob Kane with Bill Finger}}\n| Warner Bros. Pictures / DC Films\n| colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\" | Filming\n|-\n| ''[[The Suicide Squad (film)|The Suicide Squad]]''\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[James Gunn]]\n| {{based on|''[[Suicide Squad]]''|[[John Ostrander]]}}\n| Warner Bros. Pictures / DC Films / Atlas Entertainment / [[The Safran Company]]\n|}\n\n===Critical and public reception===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Film\n! [[Rotten Tomatoes]]\n! [[Metacritic]]\n! [[CinemaScore]]\n|-\n| ''Batman Begins''\n| 84% (278 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/batman_begins/ |title=Batman Begins |date=June 15, 2005 |website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=August 17, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140118065611/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/batman_begins/ |archive-date=January 18, 2014 |url-status=live |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n| 70 (41 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |