es.com/m/wonder_woman_2017 |title=Wonder Woman |website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |date=January 29, 2017 |accessdate=August 17, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170725024520/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wonder_woman_2017/ |archive-date=July 25, 2017 |url-status=live |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n| 76 (36 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/wonder-woman |title=Wonder Woman |website=[[Metacritic]] |accessdate=February 8, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180109015403/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/wonder-woman |archive-date=January 9, 2018 |url-status=live |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n| {{sort grade|A}}\n|-\n| ''Justice League''\n| 40% (377 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/justice_league_2017 |title= Justice League |website= [[Rotten Tomatoes]] |access-date= August 17, 2019 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20171119062533/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/justice_league_2017 |archive-date= November 19, 2017 |url-status=live |df= mdy-all }}</ref>\n| 45 (52 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/justice-league |title=Justice League |website=[[Metacritic]] |access-date=December 24, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117133710/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/justice-league |archive-date=November 17, 2017 |url-status=live |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n| {{sort grade|B+}}\n|-\n|''Teen Titans GO! To the Movies''\n|91% (121 reviews)<ref>{{Citation|title=Teen Titans Go! To the Movies (2018)|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/teen_titans_go_to_the_movies|language=en|access-date=2019-03-17}}</ref>\n|69 (25 reviews)<ref>{{Citation|title=Teen Titans Go! To the Movies|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/teen-titans-go!-to-the-movies|access-date=2019-03-17}}</ref>\n| {{sort grade|B+}}\n|-\n|''Aquaman''\n| 66% (374 reviews)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/aquaman_2018|title=Aquaman (2018)|work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango (company)|Fandango Media